As a user when i visit the site I’m presented with…
	a short intro on challenges
	a list of 
		challenges #
		most popular challenges
		most active users
	a link to:
		create my own challenge #
		challenge other users 
		accept a challenge #
		my profile

My profile
	list of
		accepted challenges that are still active
		successes
		failures
		other users i have challenged
		challenges other users sent me
		rewards



Models:
	User -> 
		has_many :challenges
		hbtm :accepted_challenges
		has_many :challenged_users
		has_many :owned_challenges
		has_many :my_pending_challenges
		has_many :others_pending_challenges

	challenge ->
		hbtm :challenged_users

